---
title: SignalCloud
description: Introducing a new way to ask a question and get an answer, from just about anyone, anywhere.
head_icon: /images/logo-big.png
lead: Introducing <strong>SignalCloud</strong>, a new way to ask a question and get an answer, from just about anyone, anywhere. Our tools make it easy to take intelligent, informed actions based on input from anyone with a mobile phone, world-wide.

